{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "7df906c9-1688-4734-92da-c50abc98dd31", "type": 201, "content": {"preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/7df906c9-1688-4734-92da-c50abc98dd31@1.pkg/1772597703597/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597704060", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/7df906c9-1688-4734-92da-c50abc98dd31@1.pkg/1772597703597/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597704060"}, "identifier": "7df906c9-1688-4734-92da-c50abc98dd31", "test_cases": "", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>本题考查 &ldquo;正确看待顺境和逆境&rdquo; 的知识点。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>&ldquo;沉舟侧畔千帆过，病树前头万木春&rdquo; 体现的是在逆境中不气馁，能看到发展希望并积极进取的态度。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">①</span><span>：小琳在竞选失败后积极改进，最终获得认可，符合积极面对逆境的精神；</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">③</span><span>：小桐面对作品未被选中的挫折，通过坚持练习取得进步，体现了在困境中看到希望并努力的态度，与诗句精神一致；</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">②</span><span>：小哲因失误逃避训练，是消极对待逆境的表现，不符合；</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">④</span><span>：小浩因测试失利放弃学习，属于畏惧逆境的态度，不符合；</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>答案选 B。</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": ""}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">（改编）</span><span>&ldquo;千磨万击还坚劲，任尔东西南北风&rdquo; 体现了郑板桥面对磨难仍坚韧不拔、坚守目标的精神。以下情境与之相符的是（ ）</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">①</span><span>小宇在学骑自行车时多次摔倒，却始终坚持练习，最终熟练掌握技巧</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">②</span><span>小雯在书法比赛中失利后，认为自己没有天赋，从此放弃练字</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">③</span><span>小辉在组装科技模型时遇到技术难题，查阅资料、请教老师，最终完成作品</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">④</span><span>小天在班级辩论会中因紧张发挥失常，之后再也不愿参与类似活动</span></p></div>", "label": "", "title": "（改编）“千磨万击还坚劲，任尔东西南北风” 体现了郑板桥面对磨难仍坚韧不拔、坚守目标的精神。以下情境与之相符的是（ ）①小宇在学骑自行车时多次摔倒，却始终坚持练习，最终熟练掌握技巧②小雯在书法比赛中失利后，认为自己没有天赋，从此放弃练字③小辉在组装科技模型时遇到技术难题，查阅资料、请教老师，最终完成作品④小天在班级辩论会中因紧张发挥失常，之后再也不愿参与类似活动", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {}, "time_dependent": false, "examples": {"responses": [], "feedbacks": [], "items": []}, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["B"]}], "location": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/7df906c9-1688-4734-92da-c50abc98dd31@1.pkg/item.json?v=1754984698872", "lang": "", "items": [{"min_choices": 0, "evaluate_result_show": false, "attachments": [], "columns": 1, "type": "choice", "choices_list": [], "associable_hotspots": [], "subtype": "", "children": [], "hide_answer_area": false, "options": [], "orientation": 0, "multiple": false, "raw": false, "titles": [], "rows": 1, "response_identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "0", "max_choices": 1, "gap_imgs": [], "shuffle": false, "choices": [{"identifier": "A", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"background: #FFFFFF;color: #404040;\">①②</span><span>&nbsp;</span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p></div>"}, {"identifi